Peter Jones star daga Dragons aka bar a cikin fushi bayan da talabijin show Holly Willoughby janye daga kasuwar £ 11 miliyan da salon kasuwanci alama don mayar da hankali a kan sabon kwangila da Marks & Spencer da kuma ITV
Willoughby ba ta da lokaci don alamar kayan ado da kayan haɗi Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin da ake yi da kuma alamar Goop da Gwyneth Paltrow.
