Shugaban kasa, Donald Trump ya fara wasu bukukuwa a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko na harbe-harbe guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, gami da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau, gami da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka ajiye kuri'ar da ya zaɓa don zaben a Kotun Koli, Trump ya shirya samun goyon baya ga zaben na tsaka-tsakin saboda akwai haɗarin cewa 'yan Republican za su rasa ikon su a majalisar tarayya, lokacin da za a yi kuri'u a ranar 2 ga Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi bikin Virginia na yammacin Trump a yanzu kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya shirin Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia don a yi a karfe 7 na yammacin rana, a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
