Shugaban majalisar dokokin kasar Nancy Pelosi ta ce an nada Brett Kavanaugh a kotun koli ta kasa kuma bai dace da shi ba a matsayin mai hidima a kotun koli.
Pelosi ta yi hira da jama'a a ranar Asabar a bikin Texas Tribune a Austin, Texas.
Ina bukatar in yi tunani idan wata mace ce ta yi hakan, za su yi ta'aziyya, in ji Pelosi a cikin martani ga shaidar Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Talata.
Kavanaugh ya musanta zargin da ake yi masa na yin lalata da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford da kuma matasa biyu.
A lokacin da ya bude jawabai, Kavanaugh ya kasance sosai m, kuma ya kusan bike da kuma magana da shi a kan tafi a wasu lokuta yayin da ya yi magana game da 'ya'yansa da kuma lokacinsa a makarantar sakandare.
